item.description:
@Noob.Coder wrote:

client.java:8281: illegal start of expression if (command.startsWith("ownerzone")&& playerRights >= 2)) ^ client.java:8288: illegal start of expression if(command.startsWith("pring")&& playerRights >= 2)){ //Voule Comm and Generator ^ 2 errors Press any key to continue . . .
[/quote]

If this is PI then they should be…

if (playerCommand.startsWith("ownerzone") && c.playerRights >= 2) {
if (playerCommand.startsWith("pring") && playerRights >= 2) {

A hint with compiler errors, look for the ^ symbol to tell where you went wrong. In this case it was pointing at your )) and )){ which isn’t correct, use the codes above and they should work if you’re using PI.
